data.description: Price Improvement!! This Beautiful home offers a warm & inviting atmosphere. Home boast an open floor plan with a cozy living room, tile wrapped fireplace & plenty of natural light. The kitchen boasts modern stainless steel appliances that cater to your culinary needs, a stunning slab granite countertop for a touch of luxury to the space with tile backsplash. Also offers a separate dining room with a cove ceiling & you will love the newer flooring, molding, custom blinds and paint throughout. The spacious primary bedroom comes complete with an en-suite, ceiling fan & large walk-in closet. Backyard has a patio with new fence, fresh rock & soil. Plenty of parking & no neighbors across the street. Close to shopping, dining & JBLM.
